r.ts and removes export default from others. Many files still have hardcoded col
ors (0x00aa00, 0xff4444, #ff6b6b, etc.) and old patterns.\n5. **docs/modules/cli
ent/INDEX.md not updated** - PRD-004 9.3 explicitly requires updating this file,
but no changes were made.\n\n**Minor Issues:**\n1. **designs/ vs apps/ test drif
t** - The design directory tests differ from production tests. While the design 
